edu.wpi.first.wpilibj.motorcontrol.MotorController, AutoCloseable
public class SimSparkMax extends com.revrobotics.spark.SparkMax
The `SimSparkMax` class extends `CANSparkMax` to provide enhanced simulation support for Spark MAX motor controllers. It allows you to simulate the behavior of Spark MAX motor controllers in software-based robot simulations.
